{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b (Only Bakes Time Selection)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Replaces Soundminer's "Spot through DSP Rack" functionality. Preview audio files through FX and place processed versions onto your timeline.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b How it works:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Trims to Media Explorer selection first\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Processes only selected audio through FX\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab More efficient for short clips\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b Setup:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Create track named "Media Explorer Preview"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Add FX to preview track\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Configure Media Explorer to play through preview track\par}
}

