{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Reaper Track and Item Renamer\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Batch rename items and tracks with a GUI. Supports find/replace, prefixes, suffixes, character removal, and auto-numbering with live preview.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b Features:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Find & replace text (all, first, or last instance)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Add prefixes and suffixes\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Remove characters from start or end\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Add sequential numbers with separators and zero-padding\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Live preview and auto-refresh on selection change\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b Example:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 "Guitar.wav" \'96 "SONG_Guitar_01"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b Requires:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 ReaImGui extension (available via ReaPack)\par}
}

